<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie die
                                <expan>gesworn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> des hantwerks der
                            <expan>pfist<ex>er</ex></expan> bey ewch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> fürbracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                        der heffen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und ist uns <expan>bish<ex>er</ex></expan> niht wol
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, wir <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> erfarn und ewch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<add>wissen lassen</add>, ob wir daran gemant
                        <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
